  响应曲面法优化撕裂蜡孔菌多糖的微波辅助提取工艺及抗氧化活性研究
  Study on Response Surface Methodology as an Approach for Optimization of Microwave-Assisted Extraction and Antioxidant Activities of Polysaccharides from Ceriporia lacerate
 
